edBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">今日辛苦你啦</span><br />\n真係難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能個黑工經常大大聲喺電話(用鄉下話)，同朋友講落一轉香港賺好多錢，被附近嘅洗碗大媽聽到，打1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2107dcb7c718491b37f4bea1712c181fabc03b2","tid":1007224,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4680268165d92a538a7abb7e0dd33566a9c7c7ce","tid":1007224,"uid":205462,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:52:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">今日辛苦你啦</span><br />\n真係難聽過粗口<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能個黑工經常大大聲喺電話(用鄉下話)，同朋友講落一轉香港賺好多錢，被附近嘅洗碗大媽聽到，打1823<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n報埋蘋果 有爆料費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fe885ef1420df821035455c386b4ba52637a673","tid":1007224,"uid":62815,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:55:35.000Z","msg":"擺明有人篤啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a2b50ae806b9deee28af0b30c8dc5a48f14d194","tid":1007224,"uid":191815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6660c6a301ce65155269aaef38e141a970e7000c","tid":1007224,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42bb859edbfe2276ac3a9cc79034e2cc79a467c0","tid":1007224,"uid":191815,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2cfd79f2db5f461b8451e5dc154ffa81c319bbb9","tid":1007224,"uid":232848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T16:36:13.000Z","msg":"一開始請我都無睇身分證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos